egation's arrival\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"protesters\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"his alleged role\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2010 attacks\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"the sinking\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the warship\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"an artillery strike\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"four people\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Details of the delegation's itinerary were not immediately available.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Details\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"the delegation's itinerary\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also not clear where the delegation would sit during the ceremony - a significant issue given the events of two weeks ago at the opening.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the delegation\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant issue\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There, Kim Yo Jong sat in the same VIP box with Moon and U.S. Vice President Mike Pence, creating some awkward moments.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Yo-jong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Yo Jong\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Yo-jong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Yo-jong\"}, {\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 7.870580854636795e-12, \"text\": \"M